  "original_title": "\u0bb9\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Hirunika released on bail",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Twelve people, including former Member of Parliament Hirunika Premachandra, who were arrested today while protesting in front of the Fort President's House, Colombo, have been released on police bail.",
        "Some protested with Hirunika this morning demanding that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa's government is responsible for the current crisis and that he should step down.",
        "Hirunika sat in front of the main entrance and staged a protest, chanting for the war hero Kota to come out.",
        "Hirunika said that he will stay outside the Presidential Palace until the 9th of July, when there is going to be a massive nationwide protest against the President and the government.",
        "After this, the group including Hirunika, who was arrested by the Fort police, was taken to the police bus.",
        "Meanwhile, tear gas and water cannons were used on Chetham Road on demonstrators who tried to break the barriers to the Presidential Mall."
      ],
